Discover Your True Political Identity: Find out where you shine on the political spectrum with this short political quiz. Are you a New Left Hipster? A Social Justice Crusader? The Liberal Identity Quiz will gauge everything from your taste in bumper stickers, books, and music to what you would do if you could travel through time or convene your own death panel. Share your results, and find out where your friends stand. Is your girlfriend a bigger PETA-loving tree-hugger than you knew? Does your husband base his entire worldview on The Daily Show ? This handy political quiz will help you find out. ~Political quizzes created by Daniel Kurtzman , adapted from the book How to Win a Fight with a Conservative More Political Humor:
